OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F432A1768508570
OL,3,CBristol mum's plea for 'urgent'
OL,4,Cchanges to newborn screening programme
OL,6,F"I had a traumatic delivery and Oakley
OL,7,Fstopped breathing on delivery and
OL,8,Fwithin ten days of being born, he lost
OL,9,Fa significant amount of birth-weight.
OL,11,F"He wasn't really moving in the same
OL,12,Fway that other children, something
OL,13,Fjust didn't feel right, and it's
OL,14,Falways that case around trusting your
OL,15,Fgut instinct."
OL,17,FAmy said she had to fight with doctors
OL,18,Fto take her concerns about Oakley
OL,19,Fseriously, but when they did, he was
OL,20,Fdiagnosed with the most severe form of
OL,21,FSpinal Muscular Atrophy.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
