OL,3,CBristol mum's plea for 'urgent'
OL,4,Cchanges to newborn screening programme
OL,6,FShe recalled: "I can remember the
OL,7,Fmoment sitting there in the room, even
OL,8,Fjust before he was diagnosed, the
OL,9,Fmoment we took him into hospital and
OL,10,Fthe doctors said I think this is
OL,11,Fsomething life changing and Oakley
OL,12,Fwill have to stay in hospital.
OL,14,F"I remember hearing the letters SMA
OL,15,Fand they said, 'don't research, don't
OL,16,Flook at what it means', and then when
OL,17,Fthe results came through a week and a
OL,18,Fhalf later, everything just stops,
OL,19,Feverything goes into a freeze. The
OL,20,Fstate of shock, I can't describe.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
