OL,3,CBristol mum's plea for 'urgent'
OL,4,Cchanges to newborn screening programme
OL,6,F"It essentially changed our lives
OL,7,Fforever, and obviously Oakley's too
OL,8,Fand that moment will stay with me."
OL,10,FOakley was given gene therapy which
OL,11,Fstopped his condition getting worse,
OL,12,Fbut it couldn't undo the damage
OL,13,Falready done.
OL,15,FAmy and other parents like her now
OL,16,Fwant a test for SMA added to routine
OL,17,F'heel prick' test given to all
OL,18,Fnewborns. It's a call echoed this
OL,19,Fmonth by former Little Mix star, Jesy
OL,20,FNelson, whose twin daughters were
OL,21,Frecently diagnosed.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
