OL,3,CBristol mum's plea for 'urgent'
OL,4,Cchanges to newborn screening programme
OL,6,FIt is estimated that the 'heel test'
OL,7,Fwould cost around #4 per baby to add
OL,8,Fto the current screening programme.
OL,10,FHowever, the gene therapy treatment,
OL,11,Fwhich Oakley received is expensive,
OL,12,Fand would cost the NHS more than a
OL,13,Fmillion pounds per child.
OL,15,FOne charity which is helping families
OL,16,Flike Oakley's to fundraise for
OL,17,Ftreatment and equipment not covered on
OL,18,Fthe NHS says the system is hard to
OL,19,Fnavigate for parents.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
