OL,3,CBristol mum's plea for 'urgent'
OL,4,Cchanges to newborn screening programme
OL,6,FBecky Andrew, CEO of Charity, Tree of
OL,7,FHope said: "A lot is available through
OL,8,Fpublic provision, but a lot of it is a
OL,9,Fpostcode lottery and it depends on the
OL,10,Fage of the child and things like that,
OL,11,Fit can be a really tricky time for
OL,12,Fparents navigating this."
OL,14,FBut Amy said she wishes she knew about
OL,15,Fthese options sooner.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
