OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F432A1768508570
OL,3,CBristol mum's plea for 'urgent'
OL,4,Cchanges to newborn screening programme
OL,6,F"When you know that there is something
OL,7,Fthat can be done about it and it is
OL,8,Flife changing to your child, that's
OL,9,Fthe part that I cannot accept and
OL,10,Fthat's why I'm going to shout from the
OL,11,Frooftops about this."
OL,13,FOakley is now thriving but Amy is
OL,14,Fcoming to terms with the fact that had
OL,15,Fhe been screened at birth and given
OL,16,Ftreatment earlier, things could be
OL,17,Fvery different.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
