OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F432A1768508570
OL,3,CBristol mum's plea for 'urgent'
OL,4,Cchanges to newborn screening programme
OL,6,F"He is starting to ask questions, and
OL,7,FI think the hardest part of all of
OL,8,Fthis is that one day I'm sure he'll
OL,9,Fask if anything could have been done
OL,10,Fto change things for me and what I can
OL,11,For can't do.
OL,13,F"And as a parent, knowing that things
OL,14,Fcould have been different and I will
OL,15,Fhave to explain that to him. That's
OL,16,Freally sad.
OL,18,F"Obviously I'm biased, because I'm his
OL,19,Fmum, but he is really an incredible
OL,20,Flittle boy. His sheer determination
OL,21,Fand resilience.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
